### ? VALID - Test Password Login Endpoint
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login/password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@kjn.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

###

### ? INVALID - Test with Invalid Email Format
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login/password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "invalid-email",
  "password": "admin123"
}

###

### ? INVALID - Test with Missing Password Field
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login/password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@kjn.com"
}

